# Deva.world
p:Welcom to Deva.world!

p:Deva.world is a realm for the people of the DEVA way of life.

p:Deva.world is developed from the model of the ancient RigVeda texts. Through the real you will find various Deities, Items, Hymns, and lots of Fun developed around the Vedic way of life. You can explore and make new friends from around the world who all share the same Heaven.

p:Deva.world is developed help Vedic people prepare for their entrance into the Heavenly Realms of Indra.
